==English==
===Etymology===
#Named after the original name of the science fantasy [[motion picture]] [[w:Star Wars|Star Wars: Episode IV: A New Hope]]. Also it was the name of 5 more Star Wars motion pictures, Star Wars: The Empire Strikes Back, Star Wars: Return of the Jedi, Star Wars: The Phantom Menace, Star Wars: Attack of the Clones, and the latest and last, Star Wars: Revenge of the Sith...

===Proper noun===
'''Star Wars'''

#Another name for the [[Strategic Defense Initiative]].

